casebody.data:
No. 2435. Vaughan v. Morgan.

April Term, 1889.

filed May 31, 1889. Duncan Sanders, for motion. A. B. Calvert, contra.

Order

per curiam

Motion under Rule XI. of this court to dismiss appeal for failure to file “Points and Authorities” as required by Rule VIII. Motion granted, it not appearing that such failure occurred through mistake, inadvertence, or other excusable cause.
